Description: Backup Blu-ray Disc content from the command line
 bluraybackup-ex makes a decrypted copy of a Blu-ray disc using libbluray.
 It supports two output modes selected with -m: "dir" (default) extracts the
 full disc file tree; "iso" produces a single decrypted ISO image.
 Sources can be a physical drive, an ISO/BIN disc image, or a BDMV directory.
 .
 Inspired by dvdbackup, maintained as a C17 codebase with modern CMake builds.
